# --- Frontend (Angular/TypeScript) ---
# Ignore node_modules in any subdirectory
**/node_modules/

# Ignore dist, build, .angular cache in any subdirectory
**/dist/
**/.angular/
**/.angular/cache/

# Ignore environment files (do not commit secrets!)
**/environments/environment*.ts

# Ignore coverage outputs
**/coverage/
**/coverage*.json

# --- Backend (C#/.NET) ---
# Ignore build results and publish outputs in any subdirectory
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/TestResults/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.user
**/.suo
**/.userosscache
**/.sln.docstates

# Ignore Rider, VS Code, and Visual Studio files in any subdirectory
**/.idea/
**/.vs/
**/*.suo
**/*.user
**/*.userosscache
**/*.sln.docstates

# Ignore ASP.NET generated files
**/wwwroot/

# Ignore NuGet packages
**/packages/
**/Packages/

# Ignore logs and secrets
**/*.log
**/appsettings.*.json
!**/appsettings.json

# Ignore environment variables
**/.env

# Ignore deployment artifacts
**/publish/
**/deploy/

# --- Editor & System files ---
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- NPM/Yarn/PNPM logs ---
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Global ignores ---
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp

# End of .gitignore
